{"tid":22301,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[魔性回歸]摩連奴：正在重建紅魔DNA","createTime":"2016-12-04T11:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T11:14:29.000Z","uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86a0f79710d22c4beb97b79a9570d5b89adb89b2","tid":22301,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:01:41.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=fbf5f2de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】縱使曼聯目前成績不佳，但領隊摩連奴堅稱自己正在幫助球隊尋回他們的DNA。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯周日將前往葛迪遜公園對陣愛華頓，但賽前已被榜首的車路士遠遠拋離14分，要縮窄差距，今仗不容再失。雖然自摩連奴（Jose Mourinho），紅魔成績沒有大幅提升，甚至數據顯示，較雲高爾時代更有所不及，但摩佬繼續為自己辯護，指正為紅魔尋回最強的DNA。<br />\n<br />\n「我只在乎球隊的踢法，只要對我們的方式保持信心，並嘗試爭取更好成績，一切便在季尾有分曉。」摩佬表示，「我來到這裡是打造未來，用一種特定的DNA及風格去實現目標，這是我工作的一部分，但當然還有其他的目標，就是與成績掛勾。」<br />\n<br />\n「所以，我不可能對現在的表現而高興，因為我總是對自己要求嚴格，對身邊和我工作的人也一樣，也希望球員和球會能對自己有所要求。我們現在已敢於壓過對手半場，防線壓得很前，中堅不再用人盯人戰術，而是區域聯防。世上有很多不同風格的戰術思維，但我們只要依照自己的方式，我從沒帶領過曼聯這樣能控球的球隊，也沒有帶過這麼能創造機會和控制比賽的球隊。」這位葡萄牙籍主帥續說。<br />\n<br />\n雖然聯賽已落後他人，但曼聯周中剛在英聯盃淘汰韋斯咸，成功殺入4強，有望爭奪一項盃賽錦標來加強信心。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"83116a224edefe92f2176692473128e78a74b049","tid":22301,"uid":7940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:02:40.000Z","msg":"拍大巴的DNA"},{"pid":"9c97d9f42a71524a184cda99e8840b8604e8834e","tid":22301,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:02:57.000Z","msg":"摩佬表示，「<span style=\"color: red;\">我來到這裡是打造未來</span>，用一種特定的DNA及風格去實現目標，這是我工作的一部分，但當然還有其他的目標，就是與成績掛勾。」<br />\n<br />\n未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0091c1968f79a35b1fa0f60290f639e69e688821","tid":22301,"uid":7940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>摩佬表示，「<span style=\"color: red;\">我來到這裡是打造未來</span>，用一種特定的DNA及風格去實現目標，這是我工作的一部分，但當然還有其他的目標，就是與成績掛勾。」<br />\n<br />\n未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打造熱狗二隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bfdf3eadca81cbddfca53ec6e6fb4af07baf971","tid":22301,"uid":37827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"魔性澎湃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18594c8856bf0ad62f304bd6f39195fe68d445a9","tid":22301,"uid":5386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:05:37.000Z","msg":"未來隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e464578159a66b979e9b30fab3f96110a24e142","tid":22301,"uid":23783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魔性澎湃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩 正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8855f65c35630990fc0fbdba34cbc5c9a6679c6d","tid":22301,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"將我轟dna混入去<br />\n從此獌狗正式成為我轟私家雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}